hammer  screwdriver or wrench  you need to learn what it is  what it does and when to use it  the only thing you can do is hammer  professor of educational psychology Read full profile Read full profile For more than    years  Dima Qato worked as a retail pharmacist and witnessed countless examples of the vital role pharmacies play in the public health system  particularly when it comes to access to and safe use of medications However  while many like Qato consider pharmacies to be an essential part of our health care system  the independent and chain retailers are not regulated by or held accountable to any of the groups that provide checks and balances for other essential health services  like care in hospitals and clinics Read full profile Read full profile Isabel Cruz makes sense of complex data  how to make sense of data that is collected with different spatial and temporal granularities  professor of computer science The U S  Census  for example  collects data every    years  but other population data within a city may be taken every month or year  you cannot put apples and oranges together Read full profile Read full profile Richard Novak has been working to identify therapies and vaccines for HIV since the     s  when the infection first started making the news as it spread among the gay community  That clinic opened in       and just a few years later Read full profile Read full profile What are the health effects of arsenic from drinking water and other sources  Argos examines the levels of arsenic in drinking water primarily in Bangladesh  and the associated health effects for people who live there Read full profile Read full profile  professor of medicine in the department of diabetes endocrinology and metabolism in the UIC College of Medicine  atherosclerosis and metabolism Read full profile Read full profile Terry Moore is a medicinal chemist focused on discovering new drugs to improve the lives of men and women living with chronic health conditions  l